cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "LLMedico: Automated Test Oracle Generation from Javadoc"
version: 1.0.0
date-released: 2026-04-25
authors:
  - family-names: Kroker
    given-names: Paul Jakob
license: MIT
abstract: >
  LLMedico generates test oracles (assertions) from Javadoc documentation
  of Java classes. It translates structured tags such as @param, @return,
  and @throws into executable conditions using large language models,
  enabling automated validation of program behavior.
